snippet.title: Aquaman | HD Movie Video | Queen Atlanna Love Scene | Jason Momoa,Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Movie Tittle:
Aquaman

Starring:
Jason Momoa As Aquaman,Amber Heard As Mera,Nicole Kidman As Atlanna

Director:
James Wan

Producers:
Peter Safran,RobCowan,Zack Snyder, Deborah Snyder

Story Line:
Half-human, half-Atlantean Arthur is born with the ability to communicate with marine creatures. He goes on a quest to retrieve the legendary Trident of Atlan and protect the water world.
